<ab facs="#facs_85_r2l23">man gütlıch wege <expan>darunt<ex>er</ex></expan> vinden müge / Alſo / daʒ <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade ſehe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_85_r2l24">daʒ ſie ewr etwas darynne genieſſen ſüllen / wan wo vvir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_85_r2l25"><expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gedienen <expan>möcht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir allcʒeit <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> / . <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_85_r2l26"><expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> vj̃ . <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>Remı<ex>ni</ex>ſce<ex>re</ex></expan> / . </ab>
